排文字“中央、国防部、一号首长、一分厂、二分厂” 等字样。“第一次进来的时候，邮电局的工作人员曾经试用过，都能通话。还有发电房里的发电机至今仍可以发电，现在看这些设备很落后，可在当时是最先进\r\n      的。”金文军说。 <\/font><\/b><\/i><\/font>\r\n      <p><font color=\"#1a3c1a\"><i><b><font size=\"6\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>地下指挥中心成了新景点<\/strong><\/font><\/b><\/i><\/font>\r\n      <p><font color=\"#1a3c1a\"><i><b><font size=\"6\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 据海北藏族自治州旅游局副局长北京才让介绍，该工程隐蔽、坚固、保密性强，有着极强的防御性，可保证当地面设施受到攻击时，仍能在掩体内坐镇指挥。他说，\r\n      “原子城”地下指挥中心是于4月28日正式解密开放的，是目前“原子城”景区中保存最完好、设施最齐全的一处景点，它将成为基地旅游景区中又一重要的旅游 景点。(China\r\n      Foto Press ）<\/font><\/b><\/i><\/font><\/td>\r\n    <\/tr>\r\n  <\/tbody>\r\n<\/table><\/div>\r\n<div class=doc_txt  id=\"text_67_1\" style=\"display:none;\"><\/div>\r\n","isAdminFlag":false,"isCanUpdate":false,"isDel":0,"isHide":0,"isShow":true,"keyThis":"","lDocModifiedCount":2,"LongDate":"07-05-26 23:34","online":false,"really_updated_at":"2007-08-20 19:37:56","ShortDate":"08-20 19:37","ShortDate_i":[],"ShowShInfo":"","Url":"/d52751791.u12382064.htm","UserID":12382064,"UserName":"天眼2007","UseVote":false,"v_isAdminDeleted":false,"v_isAppend":false,"v_isEditOwnDoc":false,"v_lDocModifiedPageNo":0,"v_lDocNo":66,"v_lPageCount":1.90000000000000000e+001,"v_lUserID":0,"v_lUserLevel":100,"v_SeeUserId":0},"isfirstfloor":false},{"docinfo":{},"foolrinfo":{"del_w":false,"DelTime":"","Emote":0,"fd_1_sel_product":false,"fd_id":0,"floorcontent":"<div class=doc_txt  id=\"text_68_0\"><table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"760\">\r\n  <tbody>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td colspan=\"2\" height=\"50\"><br>\r\n      <\/td>\r\n      <td colspan=\"2\" height=\"300\" valign=\"top\">\r\n      <table align=\"left\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n        <tbody>\r\n          <tr>\r\n            <td><br>\r\n            <\/td>\r\n          <\/tr>\r\n        <\/tbody>\r\n      <\/table>\r\n      <p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<font color=\"#153015\"><i><b><font size=\"7\"> 2007年5月16日：中国已经发展一种装有发动机的聪明炸弹猜测被称为KD-88。它大概如同C-802反舰导弹（21英尺长，直径360毫米，\r\n      1,500磅，连同一个360磅战斗部）相同尺寸。中国至今没有提供它用于销售，因此，缺乏详细资料。武器已经被看到被中国飞机携带。 <\/font><\/b><\/i><\/font>\r\n      <p><font color=\"#153015\"><i><b><font size=\"7\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; KD-88似乎拥有一个红外（热传感）或电视制导系统和类似在其它的导弹发现的一部涡轮喷气发动机，像YJ-83K。这样的系统看来至少射程一百公里，并\r\n      且有能力去打击小目标。一种似乎是雷达自动寻的传感器的东西已经被看到。将会安排它考虑用于打击防空系统，航空母舰或指挥部。 <\/font><\/b><\/i><\/font>\r\n      <p><font color=\"#153015\"><i><b><font size=\"7\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; KD-88大部分与较大的飞机一起出现，像JH7A。\r\n      Su-30也可以或许携带它。JH-7是一种27吨，双发动机飞机，连同一个40英尺翼展。它动力不足，而且只有一个五吨炸弹负载。但是这些新的精确武器 会充分利用\r\n      JH-7，主要被中国海军使用。飞机作战半径大约900公里，促成它有助益攻击台湾，或封锁群岛。JH7A可以携带四枚KD-88。<\/font><\/b><\/i><\/font><\/td>\r\n    <\/tr>\r\n  <\/tbody>\r\n<\/table><\/div>\r\n<div class=doc_txt  id=\"text_68_1\" style=\"display:none;\"><\/div>\r\n","isAdminFlag":false,"isCanUpdate":false,"isDel":0,"isHide":0,"isShow":true,"keyThis":"","lDocModifiedCount":2,"LongDate":"07-05-26 23:35","online":false,"really_updated_at":"2007-08-20 19:38:55","ShortDate":"08-20 19:38","ShortDate_i":[],"ShowShInfo":"","Url":"/d52751791.u12382064.htm","UserID":12382064,"UserName":"天眼2007","UseVote":false,"v_isAdminDeleted":false,"v_isAppend":false,"v_isEditOwnDoc":false,"v_lDocModifiedPageNo":0,"v_lDocNo":67,"v_lPageCount":1.90000000000000000e+001,"v_lUserID":0,"v_lUserLevel":100,"v_SeeUserId":0},"isfirstfloor":false},{"docinfo":{},"foolrinfo":{"del_w":false,"DelTime":"","Emote":0,"fd_1_sel_product":false,"fd_id":0,"floorcontent":"<div class=doc_txt  id=\"text_69_0\"><table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"760\">\r\n  <tbody>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td colspan=\"2\" height=\"50\"><br>\r\n      <\/td>\r\n      <td colspan=\"2\" height=\"300\" valign=\"top\">\r\n      <table align=\"left\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n        <tbody>\r\n          <tr>\r\n            <td><\/td>\r\n          <\/tr>\r\n        <\/tbody>\r\n      <\/table>\r\n      <p><br>\r\n      &nbsp;\r\n      <p><font color=\"#1a3c1a\"><i><b><font size=\"6\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 一部视频展现庆祝中国试飞院（CFTE）的最近成就透露大量证明中国武器计划和人民解放军空军（PLAAF）武器系统发展速度的证据。\r\n      <\/font><\/b><\/i><\/font>\r\n      <p><font color=\"#1a3c1a\"><i><b><font size=\"6\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 官方电影胶片，已经在英特网上出现，展示一种完全新级别的空对地导弹，Kh-31高速、反辐射导弹（ARM）和PL-12主动雷达超视距空对空导弹\r\n      （BVRAAM）机载发射试验，用于成都J-10和沈阳J-11B战斗机重型空对地负载，加上广泛测试和开发工作包括实际上中国服役的每架前线战斗机在 内。\r\n      <\/font><\/b><\/i><\/font>\r\n      <p><font color=\"#1a3c1a\"><i><b><font size=\"6\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 最吸引人的是一种新的导弹设计据信被指定为KD-88。一种标记为KD-88武器的几张模糊图像之前被看到但是中国试飞院（CFTE）电影显示两种截然不\r\n      同型号被西安JH-7A攻击机试验。导弹概略地是3.5米长和被一台采用下悬进气口的小型涡轮喷气/涡扇发动机提供动力。安装两种不同类型导引头―一种看 来似乎是光电（EO，可能一种成像红外导引头）而另一种或为主动雷达导引头或一种被动射频-寻的导引头。\r\n      <\/font><\/b><\/i><\/font>\r\n      <p><font color=\"#1a3c1a\"><i><b><font size=\"6\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 附原文供对照参考：\r\n      <\/font><\/b><\/i><\/font>\r\n      <p align=\"center\"><font color=\"#1a3c1a\"><i><b><font size=\"6\">China unveils\r\n      weapon developments<br>\r\n      <br>\r\n      By Robert Hewson<\/font><\/b><\/i><\/font>\r\n      <p><font color=\"#1a3c1a\"><i><b><font size=\"6\">A video produced to celebrate\r\n      the recent achievements of the China Flight Test Establishment (CFTE) reveals\r\n      a wealth of evidence for new Chinese weapons programmes and the pace of weapons\r\n      systems development by the People's Liberation Army Air Force (PLAAF). <br>\r\n      <br>\r\n      The official footage, which has now appeared on the internet, shows an entirely\r\n      new class of air-to-surface missiles, airborne launch trials of the Kh-31 high-speed\r\n      anti-radiation missile (ARM) and the PL-12 active radar beyond-visual-range\r\n      air-to-air missile (BVRAAM), heavy air-to-surface loads for the Chengdu J-10\r\n      and Shenyang J-11B fighters, plus extensive test and development activity with\r\n      virtually every front-line combat aircraft in Chinese service. <br>\r\n      <br>\r\n      Most intriguing is a new missile design believed to be designated KD-88. A\r\n      few blurred images of a weapon labelled KD-88 have been seen prior to this\r\n      but the CFTE film shows two distinct versions being trialled by Xian JH-7A\r\n      attack aircraft. The missile is roughly 3.5 m long and powered by a small turbojet/turbofan\r\n      engine with an underslung intake. Two different seeker types are fitted ― one\r\n      appears to be electro-optical (EO, potentially an imaging infrared seeker)\r\n      while the other is either an active radar seeker or a passive RF-homing seeker\r\n      for the defence suppression mission. <br>\r\n      <br>\r\n      <\/font><\/b><\/i><\/font> <b><br>\r\n      <\/b><\/td>\r\n    <\/tr>\r\n  <\/tbody>\r\n<\/table><\/div>\r\n<div class=doc_txt  id=\"text_69_1\" style=\"display:none;\"><\/div>\r\n","isAdminFlag":false,"isCanUpdate":false,"isDel":0,"isHide":0,"isShow":true,"keyThis":"","lDocModifiedCount":2,"LongDate":"07-05-26 23:36","online":false,"really_updated_at":"2007-08-20 19:40:15","ShortDate":"08-20 19:40","ShortDate_i":[],"ShowShInfo":"","Url":"/d52751791.u12382064.htm","UserID":12382064,"UserName":"天眼2007","UseVote":false,"v_isAdminDeleted":false,"v_isAppend":false,"v_isEditOwnDoc":false,"v_lDocModifiedPageNo":0,"v_lDocNo":68,"v_lPageCount":1.90000000000000000e+001,"v_lUserID":0,"v_lUserLevel":100,"v_SeeUserId":0},"isfirstfloor":false},{"docinfo":{},"foolrinfo":{"del_w":false,"DelTime":"","Emote":0,"fd_1_sel_product":false,"fd_id":0,"floorcontent":"<div class=doc_txt  id=\"text_70_0\"><table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"760\">\r\n  <tbody>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td colspan=\"2\" height=\"50\"><br>\r\n      <\/td>\r\n      <td colspan=\"2\"><span><br>\r\n      <\/span><\/td>\r\n      <td colspan=\"2\" height=\"300\" valign=\"top\">\r\n      <table align=\"left\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n        <tbody>\r\n          <tr>\r\n            <td><\/td>\r\n          <\/tr>\r\n        <\/tbody>\r\n      <\/table>\r\n      <p align=\"center\"><br>\r\n      <font color=\"#0e0e25\"><i><b><font size=\"6\"> The J-10 fighter in current service\r\n      with the PLAAF is powered by a Russian Lyulka-Saturn AL-31F turbofan engine\r\n      (Source: Chinese Internet) <\/font><\/b><\/i><\/font>\r\n      <p><font color=\"#0e0e25\"><i><b><font size=\"6\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 中国媒体在4月15日报道成都J-10战斗机“在今年内”配备一台本国-制造发动机。\r\n      <\/font><\/b><\/i><\/font>\r\n      <p><font color=\"#0e0e25\"><i><b><font size=\"6\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 依照报道，成都建立的611飞机设计所的一位资深官员最近告诉新闻媒体虽然J-10的早期生产型配备有一台国外-制造发动机用于低速率生产，战斗机会确定配备有一台中国本国的发动机，而且这可能今年进行。\r\n      <\/font><\/b><\/i><\/font>\r\n      <p><font color=\"#0e0e25\"><i><b><font size=\"6\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 现在PLA空军中服役的J-10战斗机动力由一台俄国制造Lyulka-Saturn\r\n      AL-31F涡扇发动机提供。这一种方式飞机没有俄国的同意不能够卖给国外客户。一个类似限制在另外中国制造战斗机FC-1/JF-17的销售卖方面被反 映，也使用俄国制造的发动机。为了要避免触动它最大的武器买主印度，俄国不愿意允许它的RD93发动机再出口到巴基斯坦，引起战斗机交付迟延。\r\n      <\/font><\/b><\/i><\/font>\r\n      <p><font color=\"#0e0e25\"><i><b><font size=\"6\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 中国已经超过10年发展它自己的WS-10A（商业名称：太行\r\n      （Taihang））涡扇发动机，但是计划已经遇到巨大的技术困难。发动机在2006年早期仅仅被鉴定用于设计最终确定。发动机同J-10战斗机整合据信在成都飞机公司进行中。\r\n      <\/font><\/b><\/i><\/font>\r\n      <p><font color=\"#0e0e25\"><i><b><font size=\"6\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 虽然J-10仍然已经被提供到出口市场，包括巴基斯坦、泰国和斯里兰卡等许多国家已经表示它们对这一种战斗机的兴趣。一经战斗机配备中国本国的发动机，它没有限制的能卖给任何客户。\r\n      <\/font><\/b><\/i><\/font>\r\n      <p><font color=\"#0e0e25\"><i><b><font size=\"6\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 附原文供对照参考：\r\n      <\/font><\/b><\/i><\/font>\r\n      <p align=\"center\"><font color=\"#0e0e25\"><i><b><font size=\"6\"><strong>J-10 Fighter\r\n      to be Fitted with a Chinese-Made Engine<\/strong><\/font><\/b><\/i><\/font>\r\n      <p><font color=\"#0e0e25\"><i><b><font size=\"6\">Chinese media reported on 15\r\n      April that the Chengdu J-10 fighter was to be fitted with a indigenously-built\r\n      engine \"within this year\". <\/font><\/b><\/i><\/font>\r\n      <p><font color=\"#0e0e25\"><i><b><font size=\"6\">According to the report, a senior\r\n      official of Chengdu-based 611 Aircraft Design Institute recently told the press\r\n      that although the early production variant of the J-10 was fitted with a foreign-made\r\n      engine for lower risk, the fighter would certainly be fitted with a Chinese\r\n      indigenous engine, and this was likely to happen this year. <\/font><\/b><\/i><\/font>\r\n      <p><font color=\"#0e0e25\"><i><b><font size=\"6\">Currently the J-10 fighters in\r\n      service with the PLA Air Force are powered by a Russian-made Lyulka-Saturn\r\n      AL-31F turbofan engine. This means that the aircraft cannot be sold to a foreign\r\n      customer without Russia’s consent. Such a limitation was reflected in the sale\r\n      of another Chinese-made fighter FC-1/JF-17, which also uses the Russian-made\r\n      engine. To avoid offending its biggest weapon buyer India, Russia was reluctant\r\n      to allow the fighter powered by its RD93 engine to be exported to Pakistan,\r\n      causing delays in the delivery of the fighter. <\/font><\/b><\/i><\/font>\r\n      <p><font color=\"#0e0e25\"><i><b><font size=\"6\">China has been developing its\r\n      own WS-10A (commercial name: Taihang) turbofan engine for over a decade, but\r\n      the project has encountered enormous technical difficulties. The engine was\r\n      only certified for design finalisation in early 2006. Integration of the engine\r\n      with the J-10 fighter is believed to be underway at Chengdu Aircraft Corporation.\r\n      <\/font><\/b><\/i><\/font>\r\n      <p><font color=\"#0e0e25\"><i><b><font size=\"6\">Although the J-10 has yet been\r\n      offered to the export market, many countries including Pakistan, Thailand,\r\n      and Sri Lanka have already expressed their interests in this fighter. Once\r\n      the fighter is fitted with the Chinese indigenous engine, it can be sold to\r\n      any customer without restriction.<\/font><\/b><\/i><\/font><\/td>\r\n   